Package com.distrimind.bouncycastle.jce.provider

Class X509CRLObject

java.lang.Object
java.security.cert.CRL
java.security.cert.X509CRL
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.jce.provider.X509CRLObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.security.cert.X509Extension
public class X509CRLObject
extends java.security.cert.X509CRL
Deprecated.
Do not use this class directly - either use com.distrimind.bouncycastle.cert (bcpkix) or CertificateFactory.
The following extensions are listed in RFC 2459 as relevant to CRLs Authority Key Identifier Issuer Alternative Name CRL Number Delta CRL Indicator (critical) Issuing Distribution Point (critical)
